install and setup git
 	http://help.github.com/win-set-up-git/
install and setup intellij
install standalone tomcat
	http://mirror.candidhosting.com/pub/apache/tomcat/tomcat-7/v7.0.23/bin/apache-tomcat-7.0.23.zip
	unzip to c:\git\tomcat
	create environment variable:  "CATALINA_HOME" c:\git\tomcat
	create environment variable: "JAVA_HOME" pointing to java install


